Author: gigamesh#3544
Content: how to convince Binance to reduce confs for KMD deposits? 120 confs makes it the slowest (?) coin for Binance tranfers. shouldnt dPoW alone justify a reduction?

Author: Regnar#6164
Content: should, but it's hard for them to willingly do things like that. I personally understand. As a business they take risks on accepting any coin at all, and a sure way to mitigate those risks for ALL coins is to raise conf numbers. Easier to do that than to look at each individual project and weigh risks of reducing the conf times.

Author: Regnar#6164
Content: however I don't mean we shouldn't try and get them to anyway. Just have to keep reaching out and talking about dPoW
